Now that all system fields have been turned into field objects, it would be useful to turn some of the other functions into 'fields' so that they can be performed as part of other pages.

Some operations have a very logical mapping to fields (same UI - eg link issue) - whilst others may have a different UI (eg - vote).

This would be very useful for people who want to link and log work when they resolve an issue.
